      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "どんどんぱふぱふ",
      "startTime": 6.4384802978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "一回目の開催まで、まさかこんなに時間が\n掛かっちゃうとは思わなかったね",
      "startTime": 12.1452510487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4とはいえ、お互いに忙し過ぎた……\nでも、今日こそテーマ作りを進めよう……！",
      "startTime": 19.9333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "うん。まずは二人でアイデアを出し合っていこっか\nそこから良さそうなものを選ぶ感じで――",
      "startTime": 28.2666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "startTime": 32.1648276171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ホラーにアイドル好き……\n私達らしいアイデアを沢山出せたね",
      "startTime": 37.0333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ここからテーマを決めるのは、結構大変そう\n細かいアイデアがあるのはいいんだけど",
      "startTime": 46.6666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。すずちゃんと芽衣ちゃんの曲作りを参考に\nお互いの『好き』を詰め込んでみたけど",
      "startTime": 54.5666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと出し過ぎたかも……？\n細かいアイデアもいいけど、もっと大きな枠が必要かも",
      "startTime": 60.8333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "一度、視点を変えてみてもいいかもしれないね\n例えば……私達の関係性について考えてみる、とか",
      "startTime": 69.9333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "二人の関係性……ドルオタ的にも胸アツな言葉\nライブやMVで、エモい演出が出来そうで最高",
      "startTime": 81.3333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "何か、新しいアイデアが出そうな予感……\nふわぁ……ごめん、あくびが出ちゃった……",
      "startTime": 90.3666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……。えへへ、私も……\n今日も忙しかったから、眠たくなってきちゃったね",
      "startTime": 102.4333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "アイデアは沢山出せたし、今日はそろそろ寝よっか？\n千紗ちゃん、明日は朝からお仕事だよね",
      "startTime": 111.3666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "うん……ごめんね？　せっかくデュエットの相手に\n選んでくれたのに、なかなか進められなくて",
      "startTime": 119.3666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。千紗ちゃんと一緒だったから\n沢山アイデアを出せた",
      "startTime": 127.2666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ夜遅くまで付き合ってくれて、ありがとう\nまた時間を見つけて、一緒に考えよう？",
      "startTime": 133.6666652361,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12179.058983400011,
          "startTime": 145.8457242195
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ありがとう。じゃあ、私は部屋に戻るね\nおやすみなさい、雫ちゃん。また明日",
      "startTime": 142.0999924659,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7760.001430599999,
          "startTime": 149.8599938965
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、おやすみなさい。また明日",
      "startTime": 147.0525663063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "……私も眠たいけど、まだ余裕はあるし\nもうちょっとだけ、頑張ろうかな",
      "startTime": 155.3333512305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 158.4994812493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……結局、夜遅くまでテーマ作りしてたから\nあんまり眠れなかった……",
      "startTime": 167.4333603858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "今日、千紗ちゃん、星見市でお仕事だっけ\n昨日考えたアイデア、見てもらおうかな",
      "startTime": 175.5666896502,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12099.98311999999,
          "startTime": 187.6666727702
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9866.649786599994,
          "startTime": 185.4333394368
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8084.265549999998,
          "startTime": 183.6509552002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえず、メッセを送っておこっと\nお仕事、夕方までだよね、と……他には……",
      "startTime": 183.3766439948,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
